# Ticket issue tracking

This project uses [ticket](https://github.com/wedow/ticket) (`tk`) for issue tracking — markdown files under `.tickets/`.

## Rules

- Track coordination work with `tk` per **`AGENTS.md`** §7 (never replace intent records with ad-hoc markdown TODOs in source files).
- Run `tk help` when you need command syntax.
- Commit ticket changes with related code when applicable.

## Quick reference

```bash
tk ready              # Work without unresolved deps
tk create "title"     # New ticket (prints ID)
tk start <id>         # Mark in progress
tk close <id>         # Complete
tk show <id>          # Details
tk dep <id> <dep-id>  # Dependency: id blocks until dep-id closes
```

See https://github.com/wedow/ticket for install (`brew tap wedow/tools && brew install ticket`) and migration from legacy trackers.
